name: Demon Stealth Dragon, Shiranui "Oboro"
effect: [AUTO](VC):At the beginning of your ride phase, choose up to one card from your opponent's drop, your opponent calls that card to (RC), and at the end of that turn, retires that unit.Dominate-[AUTO](VC):When your G unit [Stride], choose up to one of your opponent's rear-guards, [Stand] and dominate it, until end of turn, that unit gets [Power] +4000, and attacks your opponent's other unit.
flavor: The strong will dominate the weak. That is the principle of the world.

name: Alter Ego Messiah
effect: [AUTO](VC)[Generation Break 2]:When any locked card is unlocked, [COST][Soul-Blast 1], and draw a card.[AUTO](VC):When your G unit [Stride] during your turn, [COST][Counter-Blast 1 & lock a rear-guard], choose one of your opponent's rear-guards, lock it, choose one of your vanguards, and it gets [Power] +5000 until end of turn.
flavor: The world is me. I am the world.

name: Masked Magician, Harri
effect: [AUTO](VC)[Generation Break 2]:When this unit attacks a vanguard, choose up to one card from your soul, call it to (RC), and until end of turn, that unit and this unit get [Power] +3000.Magia-[AUTO](VC):When your G unit [Stride] during your turn, [COST][Counter-Blast 1], [Soul-Charge 1], choose up to one card from your soul, call it to (RC), and it gets [Power] +5000 until end of turn. At the end of that turn, put that called unit into your soul.
flavor: Come, let the time of dreams begin!

name: Chronojet Dragon
effect: [AUTO](VC)[Generation Break 2]:When this unit attacks a vanguard, until end of that battle, this unit gets [Power] +5000, and your opponent cannot call grade 1 or greater cards from hand to (GC).[AUTO](VC):When your G unit [Stride] during your turn, [COST][Counter-Blast 1], choose one of your opponent's rear-guards, and put it on the bottom of their deck.
flavor: The new future, starts from here.

name: Vampire Princess of Night Fog, Nightrose
effect: [AUTO](VC)[1/turn][Generation Break 2]:When your rear-guard is retired, [COST][discard three cards from the top of the deck], and you may call that retired card to (RC).[AUTO](VC):When your G unit [Stride] during your turn, [COST][Counter-Blast 1], choose up to one card from your drop, call it to (RC), and that unit gets [Power] +2000 until end of turn.
flavor: The bloodstained moon rises. It is the night of the vampire princess.
